headline: How a Strong Dollar Could Put a Lid on the Stock Market
summary: July has so far been a solid month for the dollar. The U.S. dollar index, which measures the value of the dollar against a basket of currencies, is up 1.9% this month. That’s good news considering that the dollar has been falling for almost all of this year.

headline: Sands Shopping Carnival - 4 Free Days of Family Fun Happening Now at Cotai Expo
summary: Organised by Sands China and co-organised by the Macao Chamber of Commerce, the Sands Shopping Carnival, kicked off Thursday at The Venetian® Macao with an opening ceremony attended by representatives from the government, finance, business, and community services sectors.
